Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\1c&HE0E0E0&\blur3}宇宙:陌生的面孔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}创世之初 冥冥之中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随着轰的一声{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then, bang...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}诞生了无限膨胀的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}时间 空间和物质{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在 所见超乎我们的想象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}超越了我们生存的限制{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}beyond the limits of our existence...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个空间我们称之为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in a place we call "The Universe."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们漫步在行星的地表{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They roam the planetary surface...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}穿梭于水下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}fly under water...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}翱翔在空中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and soar through the heavens.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而这不是地球上的野生动物游猎{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But this is no wildlife safari on planet Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是天文级的探险{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This is an expedition of astronomical proportions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这里看出去一切良好{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Everything looks good from here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 收到{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Okay, we copy that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一旦人类发现自己并不孤单{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When the human race discovers it is not alone...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那么我们的宇宙兄弟姐妹们都会是什么模样呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}what will our cosmic brothers and sisters look like?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了回答这个问题 主要的天文学家和太空生物学家{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To answer this question, leading astronomers and astrobiologists...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}将进化原理和物理学运用于{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}have applied the principles of evolution and physics...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有可能在宇宙中发现的五种类型的外星世界{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to five types of alien worlds likely to be found in the cosmos.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些是有可能存在的生物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}These are the creatures that could be out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}准备好 来一次星际游猎{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Prepare to take an intergalactic safari...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}睁大眼睛 来看看《陌生的面孔》{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and peer directly into the eyes of "Alien Faces."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星际庇护所{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}an intergalactic sanctuary...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}居住着数十亿个星系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of billions of galaxies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}数万亿颗恒星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and trillions of stars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}难道它只是死气腾腾的荒芜之地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Could it only be a lifeless, barren wasteland...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}到处是伽马射线暴{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of gamma-ray bursts...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}燃烧的恒星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}burning stars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}黑洞?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and black holes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抑或有生命存在于地球以外的宇宙天堂里呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Or does life exist beyond Earth in this cosmic paradise?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会不会外星人也盯着我们 琢磨着一个古老的问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Do alien faces gaze towards us, pondering the age-old question...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们孤独吗?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are we alone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}科学家仍然在搜索着{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Scientists are still searching...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们地球以外生命发来的首个信号{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}for the first signs of life beyond our planet...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是很多人相信它就在那里 等待着我们去发现{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but many are convinced it's out there, waiting for us to find it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而立足地球 要是存在的话 那会是啥模样呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But what on Earth, if anything, would it look like?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}利用地球科学 逻辑学 进化理论的有力结合{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}With a potent mix of earth science, logic, and the theory of evolution...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}计算机图形艺术家已经能够{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}computer graphic artists are able...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拿出某些外星生命的模样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to bring some of these alien faces to life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了亲眼目睹这些外星人世界{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And to come face to face with these extraterrestrial creations...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们将展开一场梦幻游猎{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we will embark on a fantasy safari...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}进入宇宙尚未探索的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}through the unexplored reaches of the universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就像是巡游在星际动物园里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}like a tourist in an intergalactic zoo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们的第一站 假设行星 Eronel{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Our first stop, the theoretical planet Eronel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}行星 Eronel是一颗年长的行星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The planet Eronel is an odd planet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}首先 它并不是围绕着我们太阳一般的恒星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}First of all, it doesn't circle around a star like our Sun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它围绕着一颗小红矮星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It circles around a little red dwarf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那些都是些小恒星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}These are tiny stars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们有时会是我们太阳大小的五分之一 六分之一{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They're sometimes a fifth, a sixth the size of our Sun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此 宜居区会非常靠近那颗恒星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So the habitable zone is going to be much closer to that star.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个宜居区是谜团的关键部分{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This habitable zone is a crucial piece of the puzzle...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}了解任何一颗行星上的生命进化的关键{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when understanding the evolution of life on any alien planet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个太阳系里的宜居区就是与恒星的距离{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A habitable zone in a solar system is the distance from the star...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在那里 水可以以液态存在于地表{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where water can exist as a liquid on the surface.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}能从恒星获得足够的热量{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It gets enough heat energy from the star...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}来获得和保留液态水{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to have liquid water and stay liquid water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}液态水是生命起源的基本元素之一{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Liquid water is one of the basic elements for life to begin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是在Eronel上 宜居区{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But on Eronel, the habitable zone...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太靠近这颗熊熊燃烧的气球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is so close to this glowing ball of burning gas...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恒星的引力将Eronel潮汐锁定{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the star's gravity causes Eronel to be tidally locked...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}极像地球的月球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}much like Earth's Moon...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们始终只能看到月球的一个面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as we only see one side of the lunar surface at all times.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这就意味着Eronel的一半始终是白天{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This would mean that half of Eronel is constantly in daylight...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而另一半始终是黑夜{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the other half is constantly in darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在中间 会有一个200英里宽的区域{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the middle, there would be a 200-mile-wide area...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}横跨南北两极{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that stretches from the north pole to the south pole...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里就是永恒的曙光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}which is in a constant state of twilight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此就会让你琢磨{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So it makes you wonder...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在这颗行星上 哪里可以发现生命呢?{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}where would we find life on this planet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}实话实说 你会发现它到处都是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, truthfully, you're going to find it everywhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是如果它是在黑暗面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But if it's on the dark side...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}生命就已经适应居住在黑暗里了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it's life that's been adapted for living in the dark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果是在明亮面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And if it's on the bright side...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}生命就已经适应就居住在明亮里了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it's life that's been adapted for living only in the bright side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而在这个曙光区{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And in this twilight zone area...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你会发现两者都适应的生物了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}you're going to find creatures that are adapted for both.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们可以在这个世界的两边自由来去{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They can wander and stray into both sides on this world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们真的把握了自己的命运{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They really control their own destinies...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去想去的地方 去想捕食的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in where they want to go and where they want to hunt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在Eronel上 你会看到有光合有机物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}On Eronel, you're going to have a photosynthetic organism...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许 有可能在海洋环境中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}probably, likely in the marine environment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}红藻或细菌{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a red alga or a bacteria...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可能适应了摄取红外线{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that will be adapted to taking in infrared light...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}摄取可以摄取的能量来充当食物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and taking what energy it can out of that and making food.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在陆地上 它或许会成为地衣之类的东西 因为天冷{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}On land, it would probably be a lichen-like thing because it's cold--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}苔藓将会适应的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}mosses that would be adapted that way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你将看到以这些为食的生物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You're going to have organisms that are going to feed off those.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Eronel上的这种藻类代表了一个很长食物链的底部{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This algae on Eronel represents the bottom of a very long food chain.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所有东西为了生存都扮演着重要的角色{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Everything plays a vital role for survival...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从植物到更大 更复杂的生物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}from the plant life to the larger, more complex creatures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在Eronel上利用这种藻类作为食物来源的一个例子{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One example on Eronel that uses this algae as a food source...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是叫做achom的昆虫{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is the insect known as an achom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}achom是一种奇怪的小生物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The achoms are a bizarre little creature.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在地球上 我们知道有所谓的形态变化{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}On Earth, we know of what we call metamorphosis.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是生物从一种形态变成另一种形态的奇怪的能力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's the odd ability of a creature to change...from one shape to another.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:06:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们看到变成蝴蝶{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We see it in butterflies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}毛毛虫 在你花园里蚕食{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A caterpillar, eating in your garden...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}爬上围墙 作茧自缚{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}will climb up on the fence, spin a cocoon...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}几个月后 破茧变成蝴蝶{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}months later, hatch out into a butterfly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些虫子也是这样 但是方法非常奇特{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}These do that, too, but they do it in a very odd way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们看上去活像鳗鱼{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They look almost eel-like...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}两排鳍分列两侧{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with two sets of fins that stick out on either side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在某些特殊的时候{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}At some peculiar moment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们爬上植物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they move over to some of the plant life...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}固定在上面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}lock themselves in...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}依附在上面 外面形成一个壳{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and attach themselves and form a shell around them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当外壳破裂时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}When that shell splits...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}出现的东西是我们前所未见的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}out comes something that we've never seen before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}攫取水中的氢气{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Taking the hydrogen from the water...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}分解氢气和氧气{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}splitting the hydrogen from the oxygen...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}充气成一个小气泡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it inflates a little bubble...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们就升出水面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and they lift right out of the water...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}微风吹拂它们 将它们带入高空{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the breezes picking them up, carrying them to high altitudes...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把它们散播到星球各地{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}spreading them out over the planet...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}随风飘到曙光区{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}towards the twilight zones as the breezes move.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们几乎就像是伞兵从天而降{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And they're almost like parachutists coming back down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一旦achom抵达地面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Once the achoms reach the ground...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们就立即建造洞穴 作为它们的住所{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they immediately create a burrow, where they primarily live.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不过在achom觅食泥土里的垃圾时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But as the achoms scavenge through the dirt for food...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们又会被食物链的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they are hunted from above...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}上一层动物从上方捕食{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}by one of the next links in the food chain...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就是peena pod{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the peena-pod.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们在这个星球上看到的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now, one of the creatures...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最有趣的动物之一就是peena pod{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that we'd find most interesting on this world is the peena-pod.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它是一种奇怪的小动物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's an odd little creature...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为它的眼睛一直绕道后面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because its eyes wrap all the way around...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以它可以看到背后的所有动静{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so it can see any movement behind it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在Eronel的曙光区{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the twilight zone of Eronel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那里会是非常阴冷{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it is going to be very dark and cold...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}原因就是其母星的光线暗淡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}due to the low light of its star...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}猎手 甚至被猎者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the hunters, or even the hunted...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都会发展出猫头鹰一般的大眼睛{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}will have developed large eyes like owls...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或像地球上的其它夜行性动物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or other nocturnal creatures here on Earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不过Eronel上的大多数动物已经发展成{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But there is an interesting adaptation...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个有趣的适应现象{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that developed in most creatures on Eronel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Eronel围绕着M星运转{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Eronel orbits an M star.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}M星发出的光大多数是红外线{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}M stars emit most of their light in infrared.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}红外线就是那种光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Infrared is the light that--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是你打开烤箱会感到热的光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's actually heat that you feel when you open up the oven.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就是这些动物能看见的光{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's what these creatures would see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们可以看到四周物体所发出的热{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They would see the heat expended by their bodies...in the world around them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它看上去完全不同于看你我{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It would look very different than it does to you or me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了看到星球的黑暗面的热信号{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}To see heat signatures on the dark side of the planet...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}赋予了Eronel上食物链最大的一环{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}gives one of the biggest links on the food chain of Eronel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}courga一个狡诈的优势{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the courga, a cunning advantage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在它们的意识 动作 集体行动的方式里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In their sense, in their moves, in the way they act together...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}活像是非洲平原上的豺狼{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they resemble jackals in the plains of Africa.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们结队而行{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They move in herds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们是猎手 它们是掠食者{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They're hunters. They're predators.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}丑陋而讨厌的动物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Ugly little, nasty creatures...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们会包围一只或一群peena pod{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that will surround a peena-pod or a colony of them...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}把它们给揪出来 作为自己的大餐{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}ferret them out, and that's their meal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们具有与众不同的能力 不管怎样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They have the odd ability, however...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不仅能在曙光区里看到东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to see not only in the twilight regions...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}用我们普通人一样的眼睛{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with eyes like we might normally have...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且它们在上方还有第二双小眼睛{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but they have a second set of smaller eyes right above...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一旦它们进入黑暗区{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that, once they move into the darker regions...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就是黑暗面{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the nighttime side...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们就可以逮住那个区域里的动物的热信号{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they can now pick up the heat signatures...of creatures in that area.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这些只是可能生活在Eronel之类的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}These are only a few of the creatures...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星球上的少数动物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that could live on a planet like Eronel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然而 至少在眼下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but, at least for now...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们只是我们想象的产物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they are simply a product of our imagination.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在科学上 我们可以坐在这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In science, we can sit there...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}想象其他地方的生命{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and we can imagine life elsewhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是要我们举例子 拿出数据点 事实上{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But if we have examples, we have one data point, in fact...{\r}
